# {tool_name} Reports

This directory contains development reports for {tool_name}.

## Naming Convention

Reports use ISO date prefix: `YYYY-MM-DD_topic.md`

## Creating a Report

```bash
TOOL ---dev report tool/{tool_name} "topic description"
```

## Content Structure

Each report should include:
- Summary (1-2 sentences)
- Changes Made (files and reasons)
- Issues Found & Fixed (root cause + lesson)
- Next Steps
